{
  "stem": "16790.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 325.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, when Crystal Night came, then she decided that she was going to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I-- it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had-- there was no money coming in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Crystal Night, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we came back to Munich to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's when my mother decided that it was time for us to, to leave Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she had heard that there was a ship that was leaving and that that ship was going to Havana, Cuba, and that you could purchase entry visas for Cuba.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had already applied for coming to this country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her twin sister was already here with her husband, who was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she made plans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She-- by, by that time, she already had sent a lot of things to her sister in New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A big box-- I remember a huge box of furniture and belongings when she-- at that time, she could still send it out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she sent that out because they had-- they came to this country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had just-- he was a doctor and didn't have too much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she sent that to him so that they could have some furnishings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in-- by 1938, she had heard about this ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had heard about the visas to Cuba.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were going to wait in Havana until our immigration quota number came up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were going to leave to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I really-- I, I remember them doing a lot of packing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a lot of packing for this huge box that was-- that was leaving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were left with very little-- and then, as we were about to leave, we packed up two suitcases.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all that we could take at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
